      <description>Margery Hall went to India on holiday in 1938 to stay with friends and
            returned again in 1939 to be married. Her husband, H.P. Hall, served in the Indian Army
            and Indian Political Service and was in India from 1938 to 1962. Margery worked in the
            Red Cross and Women's Voluntary Service during World War II. Kate Garrod is the widow of
            a Public Works Department engineer.</description>
